cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.RO

The paper discusses a model of lateral inhibition and collective perception in simple organisms without neural tissue, using a multi-agent model of slime mould. This suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well as systems and control (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MA), and robotics (cs.RO) as potential sub-categories.
